LAGOS  – The Commissioner, Accident Investigation Bureau Nigeria (AIB-N), Engr. Akin Olateru, has urged staff not to relent in pursuing excellence while delivering the bureau’s mandate of investigating air mishaps with the aim of ensuring continuous safety of air transport in Nigeria. A statement by Mr. Tunji Oketunbi, the General Manager, Public Affairs, said that the Commissioner stated this on Sunday while delivering a speech in celebration of the New Year, 2021. The statement hinted that Olateru was pleased with the bureau’s performance in the year 2020, despite the challenges of the Covid-19 pandemic and gave accolades to the staff for their various contributions. ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! Olateru, however, said that the staff must intensify efforts to continuously build a world-class and enviable institution while ensuring that focus, diligence and integrity remained their watchwords as they carry out their various duties. He also encouraged intra-department and inter-department cooperation and teamwork within the organisation as each unit, he said was important to the success of the organisation. Dangote Fertiliser Donates Classrooms, Other Facilities To Ibeju-Lekki Community AfCFTA Pact: Ramaphosa, Ahmed Applaud African Nations “Self-evaluation and self-improvement are also very important, as this is essential in ensuring everyone has a better understanding of the role they play within the organisation and how they can improve themselves to ensure continuous excellence in their service delivery, as required by our industry,” he added. The commissioner assured that personnel development and welfare, as well as the refinement of our procedures and processes would remain a priority to his administration. “It is my view that job satisfaction, equity and fairness are pivotal to high quality service delivery,” he said. In relations to the pandemic, Olateru reiterated that the crisis was yet to be over and advised everyone to be mindful and respectful of the relevant protocols, to stay safe, healthy and productive, as he wished them a safe, healthy and prosperous 2021. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION